<h2>Managing Dreamers</h2>
<div>
<h3>How do I claim a user?</h3>
<p>As a dream manager to claim a user you click the <g:img file="heart.png" width="20" height="20" /> in the other users table<br>
	on the manage dreamers tab from the dashboard.</p>
<h3>How do I create a user?</h3>
<p>Click on the <g:img file="add.png" width="20" height="20" /> in the manage dreamers tab and fill out the form. They will be<br>
	emailed a temporary password and asked to change it on login.</p>
<h3>How do I assist a user with their dreams?</h3>
<p>You assist a user with their dreams by suggesting them new dreams, or tasks for dreams,<br>
	and giving them encouragement.As well as answering their questions. </p>
<h3>How do I accept/reject to manage a user?</h3>
<p>You click on the <g:img file="accept.png" width="20" height="20" /> or <g:img file="reject.png" width="20" height="20" /> next to their name.</p>
